1. Juče se *pojavila* nova epizoda omiljene serije. (Yesterday, a new episode of my favorite show *appeared*.)

2. Očekuje se da će se uskoro *pojaviti* novi model telefona. (It is expected that a new phone model will *appear* soon.)

3. Kada se prvi put *pojavio* na televiziji, postao je hit. (When he *appeared* on television for the first time, he became a sensation.)

4. Ne znam kako se to *pojavilo* u mom ormaru. (I don't know how that *appeared* in my closet.)

5. Oni su se neočekivano *pojavili* na sastanku. (They unexpectedly *appeared* at the meeting.)

6. Slika se polako *pojavljivala* na ekranu. (The picture was slowly *appearing* on the screen.)

7. Problemi su se *pojavili* tek nakon nekoliko meseci. (The problems *appeared* only after a few months.)

8. Kada će se novi film *pojaviti* u bioskopima? (When will the new movie *appear* in theaters?)

9. Uvek se neko iznenada *pojavi* kada je najmanje očekujemo. (Someone always *appears* suddenly when we least expect it.)

10. Izgleda da se problem neće *pojaviti* uskoro. (It seems that the problem won't *appear* soon.)